## ‚ú® Text Formatting

- **Emphasis**: Use single asterisks for *italics* (`*italic*`) and double asterisks for **bold** (`**bold**`).
- **Links**: Brackets for link text should not have leading or trailing spaces.

**Good Example**:

```markdown
This is **important** and should be read *carefully*.

[Google](https://www.google.com)
```

**Bad Example**:

```markdown
This is __important__ and should be read _carefully_.

[ Google ](https://www.google.com)
```
